Yao Sheng used dyes imported from France.

26
00:02:27,930 --> 00:02:33,170
The textiles they produce are okay, <br> but their price is 10 percent cheaper than ours.

27
00:02:33,170 --> 00:02:35,730
However, the cost of importing dyes is expensive.

28
00:02:35,730 --> 00:02:38,390
How could their textiles be cheaper than ours?

29
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:41,530
I think that Yao Sheng is disregarding costs,

30
00:02:41,530 --> 00:02:44,180
and doing cut-throat competition.

31
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:50,200
Have someone look up Yao Sheng's backing. <br> Also, take a look and see how much money we have left in our account.

32
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:53,920
We must defeat them this time.

33
00:02:55,290 --> 00:02:57,160
Yes.

34
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:15,900
Shao Tian.

35
00:03:18,830 --> 00:03:21,940
What's wrong? Why do you look hassled?

36
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:26,610
Shao Tian. Listen to me. I just transferred the money out.

37
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:29,790
Wu Hong Da suddenly wants to check the balance of the accounts.

38
00:03:29,790 --> 00:03:32,630
He says it's to deal with the cut-throat competition.

39
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:35,940
Tell me what we should do.

40
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:42,280
It was such a big sum of money and you dared to steal it. <br>It's causing a stir now.

41
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,960
You're so scared that you're about to piss.

42
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:47,480
If they investigate the huge sum of money, we will be in trouble.

43
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:51,690
You don't know Wu Hong Da. He is very cruel.

44
00:03:51,690 --> 00:03:55,190
Of course, I know what kind of person he is.

45
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:58,610
I schemed about this money for a long time.

46
00:03:58,610 --> 00:04:00,620
Don't worry.

47
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:05,610
I'm his eyes. You are his hands.

48
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:10,290
We know very well what actions he will take.

49
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:13,700
Shao Tian. Didn't you say that we would leave Huzhou once the money was in our hands?

50
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:16,040
