Very soon.

52
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:23,040
I have a plan. Don't be impulsive.

53
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:29,020
Shao Tian. The money will be in our hands soon. <br>Why aren't we leaving?

54
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:33,900
