55
00:04:33,900 --> 00:04:36,390
You want to be their son-in-law?

56
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:38,930
I'm saying, Shao Tian. Stop dreaming.

57
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:44,770
If Miss knew you are scheming with her father behind her back, <br>she would chew and spit you out in a second.

58
00:04:53,570 --> 00:04:56,260
Don't get involved in my affairs.

59
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:58,370
I know what to do.

60
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,870
Have you seen this person?

61
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:08,140
No.

62
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:10,570
Hello. Have you seen this person?

63
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:13,420
Okay, you can leave first.

64
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:15,710
Manager Jiang.

65
00:05:19,730 --> 00:05:23,480
Madam Jiang's illness is not stable. It's worse than before.

66
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:26,390
And there wasn't any symptoms before her illness started.

67
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:29,510
We, the medical staff, have been trying our best to help her,

68
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:32,240
but have had little success.

69
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:36,870
When she is discharged, you and Miss Fang must work hard to persuade her.

70
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:40,970
Perhaps, she might accept the advice of her family members.

71
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:45,990
It has been many years. When my mom thinks of unhappy events,

72
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:48,560
she becomes like this.

73
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:52,430
We have tried many methods and consulted many doctors

74
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:55,270
but there is no progress.

75
00:05:57,470 --> 00:06:00,410
Mom. What are you doing?

76
00:06:00,410 --> 00:06:01,690
Give me the scissors.

77
00:06:01,690 --> 00:06:05,920
Yu Er. I don't want to live anymore.

78
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:09,170
If I die, you don't have to suffer so much.

79
00:06:09,170 --> 00:06:13,840
Madam Jiang. Let's talk it over. Your son is here.

80
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:17,240
- Don't do anything foolish.<br>- It's useless.

81
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:20,060
They forced my husband to die.

82
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:23,550
They are thinking of forcing me and the Wu family.

83
00:06:23,550 --> 00:06:25,710
- Mom. <br>- Don't move.

84
00:06:25,710 --> 00:06:29,020
Okay, I won't move. Don't do anything either.

85
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:31,160
Don't move.

86
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:35,380
You have suffered for the past few years.

87
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:40,000
I didn't take good care care of you. Instead, you had to take care of me instead.

88
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:46,360
When I'm dead, you don't have use your savings to treat me.

89
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:49,730
I really can't drag you down any longer.

90
00:06:49,730 --> 00:06:52,050
Mom, don't say this. You are not dragging me down.

91
00:06:52,050 --> 00:06:54,360
When I die,

92
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,410
I can be free. You can be free too.

93
00:06:57,410 --> 00:06:59,460
Aunt.

94
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:05,370
Mom.

95
00:07:05,370 --> 00:07:08,960
Doctor, help me to treat her wound.

96
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:13,580
Aunt. You said that you wanted to be free and didn't want to drag anyone down.

97
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:18,620
Actually, you are trying to run away and using the pain as your excuse.

98
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:24,810
