103
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,060
You are also leaving all your pain to them.

104
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:43,970
They will never be able to forgive you and themselves.

105
00:07:44,810 --> 00:07:50,040
Four years ago, my mom and I were in the same situation as you.

106
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:55,650
