111
00:08:13,710 --> 00:08:16,500
No one will disturb you again.

112
00:08:19,990 --> 00:08:23,740
Everything should be alright. Take a rest soon.

113
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:36,520
Nurse. Where is the outpatient clinic?

114
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,150
Over there.

115
