149
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:30,600
If you find out my name, I will then reconsider if I should give it to you.

150
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,670
- Rotten Stone Head. <br>- And also,

151
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:35,360
