153
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:40,850
If not, I will sue them.

154
00:11:40,850 --> 00:11:44,750
I don't need to ask them. I already know your rotten name.

155
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:50,850
It's Rotten Stone Head.

156
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,960
Brother Shao Tian, why are you here?

157
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,670
I went to your house to look for you. They told me that you were at the hospital.

158
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:11,580
I witnessed your heroic deed in saving someone.

159
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:15,390
Our little heroine is injured. Let me bandage your wound.

160
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:17,970
It's already done.

161
00:12:18,950 --> 00:12:21,550
That fast?

162
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:26,510
-Who was that man? <br>-Are you referring to Rotten Stone Head?

163
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:29,490
He is the guy who snatched my pen.

164
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:48,940
Cai Hong, I like you.

165
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:52,620
I want to take you for my wife.

166
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:04,930
Cai Hong. You don't need to answer me right now.

167
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,620
You really don't need to.

168
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,620
You just need to know that in this world,

169
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:11,690
there is always someone waiting for you by your side.

170
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:15,990
No matter when or where, no matter the circumstances,

171
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:19,420
I will always be waiting for you.

172
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:33,020
Brother.

173
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:41,310
Here's today's newspaper. It has news about Ling Long.

174
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:56,130
Petty devil. Petty devil.

175
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:58,330
You're really narrow-minded.

176
00:13:58,330 --> 00:14:00,610
I saved your mom

177
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:03,760
and you still won't let me have the pen.

178
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:07,900
I should visit his mom but I hit her yesterday.

179
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:10,980
Would she remember and hate me?

180
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:17,050
No. In order to give my Dad a surprise, I must find out his name.

181
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:22,850
Wu Long.

182
00:14:22,850 --> 00:14:27,910
Kitty, I don't have time to play with you today. <br>I have a very important task to do.

183
00:14:27,910 --> 00:14:31,970
See you later. Keep the rabbit company.

184
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:45,280
Who is it?

185
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:47,430
Come in.

186
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:50,010
Aunt.

187
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:51,490
It's you.

188
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:54,570
-Don't get up. <br>-Come here.

189
00:14:55,850 --> 00:14:58,700
Lie down. Don't get up.

190
00:14:58,700 --> 00:15:01,090
Come and sit.

191
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:05,800
Aunt, sorry about yesterday.

192
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:08,910
I'm here to apologise to you today.

193
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:12,100
You really don't need to apologise to me.

194
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:17,110
Yesterday, fortunately, you slapped me and made me come to my senses.

195
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:21,710
Otherwise I would still be bashing my head against a brick wall.

196
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:26,950
Actually, I have been hurting my family all these years.

197
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:33,410
Once I'm discharged, I will treat you to a meal.

198
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:38,750
I don't need the meal but if you really want to thank me,

199
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:41,970
you can tell me your son's name.

200
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:46,430
If you have any matters with him, you can wait for him to come later.

201
00:15:46,430 --> 00:15:49,670
Why don't you ask him yourself?

202
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:58,960
He won't tell me when he sees me.

203
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,330
Why?

204
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,940
It's a long story.

205
00:16:05,730 --> 00:16:08,010
Hello, Mr Jiang.

206
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,710
Mom.

207
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,360
Mom.

208
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:21,510
You are here.

209
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:22,790
Mom, what are you doing?

210
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:26,980
I'm tired of lying down and wanted to move around.

211
00:16:36,970 --> 00:16:39,670
Yu... Jiang Yu.

212
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:43,580
Is your work done at the factory?

213
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:50,580
Jiang Yu. If you are busy, you don't need to visit me.

214
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:54,620
I'm fine.

215
00:16:56,780 --> 00:17:01,740
Son, don't worry. I'm really fine.

216
00:17:01,740 --> 00:17:04,040
Mom, are you really okay?

217
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:19,030
What are you doing?

218
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:22,500
Mom. What is she doing here?

219
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:27,850
What are you both doing?

220
00:17:27,850 --> 00:17:29,630
We didn't do anything.

221
00:17:29,630 --> 00:17:33,410
I only promised her that I would call your name.

222
00:17:33,410 --> 00:17:37,970
I already know your name. <br>It's Jiang Yu.

223
00:17:39,890 --> 00:17:41,980
Let's go.

224
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:43,520
Let's go.

225
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:48,000
I only just called his name. What's wrong?

226
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:52,970
Take this.

227
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:56,640
Where is my fountain pen?

228
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:59,430
Don't you remember what I said the other time?

229
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:03,240
I said that once you found out my name, we would discuss this again.

230
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:07,350
I didn't promise that I would give you the pen immediately.

231
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:12,900
Rotten Stone Head. A kid knows what a promise is.

232
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:16,470
You are going to be a scoundrel over a pen?

233
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:18,170
Even I feel ashamed for you.

234
00:18:18,170 --> 00:18:20,660
Okay. Even if I promised to give you the fountain pen,

235
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:24,270
it was agreed on that you couldn't spend any money.

236
00:18:24,270 --> 00:18:28,090
You bribed my mom. You broke the pact first.

237
00:18:28,090 --> 00:18:30,630
When did I bribe your mom?

238
00:18:30,630 --> 00:18:34,480
Did you make this appear from thin air?

239
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:38,290
This is to declare my sincerity. That's why I bought this for her.

240
00:18:38,290 --> 00:18:40,040
I didn't have any intentions to bribe her at all.

241
00:18:40,040 --> 00:18:43,950
In any case, I have only two words. Definitely not.

242
00:18:43,950 --> 00:18:47,520
Then I also have two words. Shame-less.

243
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:53,730
Okay. Seeing how pitiful and miserable you are,

244
00:18:53,730 --> 00:18:58,390
I will give you another chance. Don't spend a single cent or go through my mom,

245
00:18:58,390 --> 00:19:00,980
just find out my favourite food.

246
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:04,790
I will consider whether to let you have the pen then.

