00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,520
Jiang Yu. You don't keep your promise.

248
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:12,970
I don't believe that I can't find the exact same pen.

249
00:19:12,970 --> 00:19:17,220
Miss. There was really only one of that pen. I'm not lying to you.

250
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:20,510
There is only one in Huzhou. It can't be that there is also only one in this world.

251
00:19:20,510 --> 00:19:23,370
Miss. If you really like that fountain pen,

252
00:19:23,370 --> 00:19:26,550
I can send a telegraph to the overseas manufacturer to order another one,

253
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:29,600
but it will take a long time. It takes around twenty days.

254
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:33,950
Twenty days? My father's birthday celebration is in ten days. It will be too late for me.

255
00:19:33,950 --> 00:19:36,270
Why don't you look around my shop for another gift?

256
00:19:36,270 --> 00:19:39,980
I don't want to. I only want that fountain pen.

257
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:53,380
<i>I will treat you to a meal another day. What do you like to eat?</i>

258
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:55,500
<i>I can treat you to anything.</i>

259
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:57,090
Stop the rickshaw.

260
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:05,350
It's really you.

261
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:09,180
Come. What are you doing here?

262
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:11,980
Where is your fierce owner?

263
00:20:13,970 --> 00:20:17,890
Did you leave home? Are you afraid of her too?

264
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:22,980
Why don't we do this? I will take you to visit my home.

265
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:25,590
Okay, let's go.

266
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:31,720
Brother. What are you doing?

267
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:35,280
A cat is here. So cute.

268
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:37,990
-I picked it up. <br>-You picked it up?

269
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:41,360
This is not something you would usually do.

270
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:45,000
- You don't like animals, right? <br>- Who says so?

271
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:51,030
So cute.

272
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:57,150
Don't play with her anymore. <br>Go to the kitchen and find her something to eat and drink.

273
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:59,450
- Okay. <br> - Go now.

274
00:20:59,450 --> 00:21:02,930
Are you hungry?

275
00:21:15,630 --> 00:21:20,040
Meow, it's time to eat.

276
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,990
Wu Long, it's time to eat.

277
00:21:28,010 --> 00:21:30,930
Wu Long?

278
00:21:30,930 --> 00:21:33,980
Transfer the money back.

279
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:37,380
- What? <br>- Transfer the money back.

280
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:39,370
You...

281
00:21:39,370 --> 00:21:42,930
Are you saying to transfer the money back to the company?

282
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:46,430
Yes.

283
00:21:46,430 --> 00:21:48,840
Transfer the money back to Ling Long.

284
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:50,740
No. Shao Tian, what do you mean?

285
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:54,970
At first, I didn't want to touch the money but you forced me to do it. <br>You are reversing it now.

286
00:21:54,970 --> 00:21:58,920
You are not playing with Wu Hong Da. You are playing with me.

287
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:04,200
Just do what I tell you to do.

288
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:07,820
You don't have the right to discuss terms with me.

289
00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:14,000
I don't care what methods you use. Transfer the money back discreetly.

290
00:22:16,990 --> 00:22:19,150
Once it's done,

291
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:22,740
I won't treat you unfairly.

292
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:27,490
Okay, I will do according to what you say

293
00:22:27,490 --> 00:22:30,330
but Shao Tian, you should know that

294
00:22:30,330 --> 00:22:34,380
for such a huge sum of money, it's not easy to move it.

295
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:37,400
Now that we are going to transfer it back, it will create problems.

296
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:42,430
Such a huge amount cannot appear from nowhere. We need to have some kind of contract or something else.

297
00:22:42,430 --> 00:22:45,760
I think we should find a suitable time.

298
00:22:47,950 --> 00:22:50,060
Take action fast

299
00:22:50,060 --> 00:22:53,390
before Wu Hong Da finds out.

300
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:58,990
I will assist you when necessary.

301
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,360
Brother.

302
00:23:15,360 --> 00:23:17,680
We received news about Ling Long.

303
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:20,020
They said that the company is in trouble.

304
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:24,590
They had problems with generating their normal turnover. People are starting to complain.

305
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:27,400
Relay this instruction down. Starting from now,

306
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:30,450
we will offer basic unit prices for all small customers

307
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:34,580
and immediate execution of the given orders.

308
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:38,950
This will help us to win over Ling Long's small customers

309
00:23:38,950 --> 00:23:41,630
and completely dry off their cash flow.

310
00:23:41,630 --> 00:23:45,550
Wu Hong Da will no longer be considered so almighty.

311
00:23:47,770 --> 00:23:58,260
<i>Timing and subtitles brought to You by Gone with the Shirt Team @ Viki</i>

312
00:23:59,710 --> 00:24:01,790
Come in.

313
00:24:02,260 --> 00:24:05,910
Boss. This lady said that she's your friend.

314
00:24:05,910 --> 00:24:07,090
Miss Lu Man.

315
00:24:07,090 --> 00:24:11,370
I have not seen the handsome face of Boss Wu for few days now.

316
00:24:11,370 --> 00:24:15,670
Miss Lu Man's visit graces our humble home. Is Master Lu in good health?

317
00:24:15,670 --> 00:24:18,700
In very good health. When he knew I was paying you a visit today,

318
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:22,020
he especially instructed me to send his regards to you.

319
00:24:22,020 --> 00:24:24,980
Shao Tian. Go back to work first.

320
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:26,070
Okay.

321
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:28,830
Miss Lu. This way, please.

322
00:24:33,150 --> 00:24:35,550
Please sit.

323
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:38,730
Miss Lu. Why are you looking for me?

324
00:24:38,730 --> 00:24:42,930
I heard that you ran into a small problem.

325
00:24:43,810 --> 00:24:47,090
Other people are eyeing Ling Long with curiosity.

326
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:50,610
There is a cashflow problem in your company.

327
00:24:50,610 --> 00:24:54,970
Will those problems not turn Ling Long into a chopping board?

328
00:24:57,030 --> 00:25:02,040
I might have a perfect solution for your current problems, Boss Wu.

329
00:25:02,710 --> 00:25:06,130
Ling Long definitely has a small problem lately

330
00:25:06,130 --> 00:25:09,540
but it's still better that we solve it ourselves.

331
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:14,270
Boss Wu, the whole Huzhou city is dominated by Master Lu.

332
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:16,650
Nothing can escape my eyes.

333
00:25:16,650 --> 00:25:20,950
Miss Lu. Why do you want to help me?

334
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:24,500
You are a smart man.

335
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,990
I'm here today

336
00:25:27,690 --> 00:25:32,490
to use this cheque to buy something.

337
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:43,020
What do you want to buy?

338
00:25:43,020 --> 00:25:46,000
Ling Long's trade secrets.

339
00:25:51,180 --> 00:25:55,660
All of Ling Long's dye recipes are made public.

340
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:58,350
I don't have any trade secrets.

341
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:02,290
Boss Wu.

342
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:05,230
I am getting bored by this childish play.

343
00:26:05,230 --> 00:26:08,360
What I want is not your trade secrets,

344
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:11,450
but the secrets of the Jiang family.

345
00:26:13,630 --> 00:26:15,990
<i>You are dreaming.</i>

346
00:26:26,930 --> 00:26:31,870
Miss Lu Man, I am grateful for your kindness,

347
00:26:31,870 --> 00:26:34,600
but I really don't have any trade secrets.

348
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:38,990
I have never heard of this.

349
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:44,270
Maybe Boss Wu is just not willing to part with it yet.

350
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:46,190
So be it then.

351
00:26:46,190 --> 00:26:51,140
I would also frown if you'd give away such precious things so quickly.

352
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:53,420
This is my phone number.

353
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:57,350
If you change your mind, please call me.

354
00:26:57,350 --> 00:27:00,970
We can discuss the price.

355
00:27:16,910 --> 00:27:18,990
Brother.

356
00:27:21,990 --> 00:27:24,510
What's wrong?

357
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:26,820
These acounts are giving me a headache.

358
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:29,680
There are some which I can't balance. Please help me to take a look.

359
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:32,330
Where? Let me see.

360
00:27:32,330 --> 00:27:34,490
It's here.

361
00:27:34,490 --> 00:27:38,050
This money is from Henghua Cloth Square, coming through with the start-up funds.

362
00:27:38,050 --> 00:27:42,250
We have agreed on two points per annum, giving them 3 years to pay us off.

363
00:27:42,990 --> 00:27:46,050
Then in what tables should I put it?

364
00:27:46,050 --> 00:27:50,100
I have taught you this so many times already. They go into the receivable accounts.

365
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:53,050
Here.

366
00:28:23,250 --> 00:28:26,850
<i>I don't want anything except this.</i>

367
00:28:26,850 --> 00:28:31,610
<i>I have never seen such a rude, stingy and mannerless man like you!</i>

368
00:28:31,610 --> 00:28:39,450
<i>You see, he has a strikingly handsome face. <br> He has a Grecian nose, strong brows and bright-eyed, with an uncommon demeanor.</i>

369
00:28:39,450 --> 00:28:44,000
<i>No matter how you look at him, upon meeting you'll fall for him, he is definitely a very handsome man.</i>

370
00:28:52,820 --> 00:28:57,200
<i>Brother, I spent my most beautiful days in the shelter provided by the Jiang family.</i>

371
00:28:57,200 --> 00:29:00,980
<i>You didn't abandon me during my most difficult times.</i>

372
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:06,030
<i>In your eyes, I'm so stupid. I can't even do the accounts.</i>

373
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:09,600
<i> I will still allow you to teach me.</i>

374
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:12,040
What's wrong?

375
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:15,940
Are you blaming me for not taking you to find your owner?

376
00:29:17,980 --> 00:29:21,980
Okay.

377
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:25,990
I will take you to find her tomorrow. Okay?

378
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:35,820
It's just a darn fountain pen. What's so great about it?

379
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:39,210
I will knit this scarf myself.

380
00:29:39,210 --> 00:29:42,580
In my Dad's eyes, it will be priceless.

381
00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:45,680
Miss.

382
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:52,430
I searched everywhere since yesterday and I can't find Wu Long.

383
00:29:52,430 --> 00:29:55,440
Could she really be lost?

384
00:29:57,730 --> 00:30:00,320
- Cai Hong. <br>- Brother Shao Tian.

385
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:03,300
- Wu Long is missing. I'm going to find her. <br>- I will go with you.

386
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:05,990
Let's go then.

387
00:30:18,650 --> 00:30:22,830
How are we going to find your owner?

388
00:30:24,250 --> 00:30:28,310
If I can't find her, I will rear you forever. I'm not bad as your owner either.

389
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:32,980
Okay, I know. Let's just wait a while longer.

390
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:35,020
Wu Long.

391
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:38,100
Wu Long.

392
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:40,410
Wu Long.

393
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:43,760
Wu Long.

394
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:47,870
Cai Hong. I already looked over there. I can't find her.

395
00:30:47,870 --> 00:30:52,340
Wu Long went out with me. She must be near the hospital.

396
00:30:52,340 --> 00:30:55,070
She can't really be lost.

397
00:30:55,710 --> 00:30:58,940
Look at how anxious you are. Your head is full of sweat.

398
00:31:03,870 --> 00:31:07,670
I will do it myself.

399
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:13,020
Let's go home.

400
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:20,020
<i>Jiang Mansion </i>

401
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:41,620
Stop the rickshaw.

402
00:31:47,190 --> 00:31:49,370
Forget it. No need.

403
00:31:51,410 --> 00:31:53,960
Wait.

404
00:31:57,250 --> 00:31:59,100
Do I know you?

405
00:31:59,100 --> 00:32:01,800
- What's wrong with you? <br>- Nothing.

406
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:04,010
- Don't you want the pen? <br>- No.

407
00:32:04,010 --> 00:32:07,270
- Do you want the cat then&gt; <br>- No!

408
00:32:07,270 --> 00:32:10,050
Are you talking about Wu Long?

409
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:14,840
This is not a new game of yours, right?

410
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:17,270
It's up to you whether you believe me or not.

411
00:32:17,950 --> 00:32:20,010
I believe you.

412
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:25,070
If you do this, wouldn't your boyfriend be unhappy if he sees?

413
00:32:27,410 --> 00:32:28,960
First, I don't have a boyfriend.

414
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:35,100
Secondly, if I had a boyfriend, he would not like you to be so stingy.

415
00:32:35,100 --> 00:32:37,790
The cat is at my home but...

416
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:42,670
Must I find out what's your favourite food or must I find out where you live?

417
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:44,870
What I wanted to say was...

418
00:32:44,870 --> 00:32:48,690
I don't have time today but tomorrow is fine.

419
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:53,670
Okay, state the meeting place and time.

420
00:32:53,670 --> 00:32:57,330
Then tomorrow at 3pm at Chaoyin Bay Bridge.

421
00:32:57,330 --> 00:33:00,060
Okay, it's 3pm then. Don't break the appointment.

422
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:04,520
If you do, I'm going to throw your cat into the river to feed the fish.

423
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:06,960
See if you dare!

424
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:11,660
Let's go.

425
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,290
Why did you call me here?

426
00:33:15,290 --> 00:33:18,670
Shao Tian. There is a big problem.

427
00:33:18,670 --> 00:33:21,370
Wu Hong Da has been conducting investigations for the past few days.

428
00:33:21,370 --> 00:33:24,940
He told everyone to move the ledger books to his office.

429
00:33:28,330 --> 00:33:30,190
Think of a solution.

430
00:33:30,190 --> 00:33:33,030
How can I think of a solution?

431
00:33:33,030 --> 00:33:36,620
Shao Tian. All the ledger books are locked inside his safe.

432
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:39,000
He is the only one who knows the combination to the safe.

433
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:41,320
He already doesn't trust me.

434
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:45,320
I already feel like he is aware of this matter.

435
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:48,920
It's all your fault. We would have left with the money.

436
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:52,360
Who would have thought this would come back to bite us one day.

437
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:56,910
Don't expect me to fix it. You are the only one who can get those books.

438
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:03,930
Tomorrow is Wu Hong Da's 40th birthday celebration.

439
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:07,130
He will definitely have a banquet in his mansion.

440
00:34:07,130 --> 00:34:13,050
There will be many people. He definitely keeps the ledger books in the company.

441
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:21,970
We will take action tomorrow.

442
00:34:25,930 --> 00:34:27,640
Look.

443
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:29,930
It's really beautiful. Did you draw this?

444
00:34:29,930 --> 00:34:31,940
You really drew this?

445
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:35,140
Is this me?

446
00:34:35,140 --> 00:34:38,270
- Do I look young? <br>- Younger by five years.

447
00:34:38,270 --> 00:34:39,500
I really look young.

448
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:42,190
Dad is always a young hero in my eyes.

449
00:34:42,190 --> 00:34:44,620
This is a drawing of the entire Wu family.

450
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:48,070
If the future, when you go out for business, you can take this along with you.

451
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:51,750
It will seem like your whole family is with you.

452
00:34:51,750 --> 00:34:54,910
Great.

453
00:34:54,910 --> 00:34:56,590
By the way, where is your sister?

454
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:59,210
Is she sleeping late again?

455
00:34:59,210 --> 00:35:01,150
This wench.

456
00:35:02,220 --> 00:35:05,700
Who drew this? I already heard.

457
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:11,230
Dad, today's your birthday. I wish you all the best, joy and peace.

458
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,410
Here's your present.

459
00:35:12,410 --> 00:35:15,950
Sister's present is a high end product. My drawing can't be compared it.

460
00:35:15,950 --> 00:35:19,050
That may not be so.

461
00:35:19,050 --> 00:35:20,710
Here.

462
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:22,880
Dad, take a look.

463
00:35:26,260 --> 00:35:28,230
This is...

464
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:30,830
I personally made this scarf.

465
00:35:30,830 --> 00:35:32,650
For me?

466
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:35,990
- I thought it was for Shao Tian. <br>- Yes, me too.

467
00:35:35,990 --> 00:35:39,540
Let me try it. So how?

468
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:42,490
It's the first time Cai Hong knitted anything. It's really not bad.

469
00:35:42,490 --> 00:35:45,600
Dad. In the future, I will knit a better one for you.

470
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:49,780
This is already good enough. I like it.

471
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:54,910
Dad. I can knit a scarf for you now. In the future, I will cook for you.

472
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:59,000
I will also help you in your business, when you are too old to do it by yourself.

473
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:03,000
And I will stick to your side through thick and thin.

474
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:06,530
Anyways, father, please look forward to your daughter taking care of you.

475
00:36:06,530 --> 00:36:08,410
Okay, I will be waiting for it.

476
00:36:08,410 --> 00:36:11,650
Dad, I can do it too. In the future, I will be filial to you too.

477
00:36:11,650 --> 00:36:13,760
Okay, I will be waiting for the both of you.

478
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:17,220
Look at how filial they both are. The weather's hot. Take it off.

479
00:36:17,220 --> 00:36:21,390
No. Cai Hong gave this to me. I must wear it every day.

480
00:36:21,390 --> 00:36:26,320
I'm going to the factory for a while. There are some matters I need to settle.

481
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:29,530
Dad. Today is your birthday. Can't you give yourself a day off?

482
00:36:29,530 --> 00:36:32,440
That's right. Even the workers in the factory thought that you were taking a day off for your birthday.

483
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:35,460
What's so urgent that you have to settle it yourself?

484
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:38,480
I made an appointment with a very important person.

485
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:41,140
I will be back for the birthday celebration.

486
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:43,230
Come home early then.

487
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:45,970
Dad, take care.

488
00:36:45,970 --> 00:36:48,390
You both, listen to me.

489
00:36:48,390 --> 00:36:51,500
Regarding this banquet...

490
00:37:05,860 --> 00:37:10,030
No, move it a bit.

491
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:18,250
Mom. What's wrong?

492
00:37:18,250 --> 00:37:22,200
I'm anxious. Look, the guests are already here.

493
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:24,190
Your father is still not back yet.

494
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:27,290
Dad is too much. Once he's busy with work, he forgets everything.

495
00:37:27,290 --> 00:37:30,810
